instructions: Put the plate on the charger
Set napkin on top of plate
Put dinner form with prong facing up on the left side of the charger
set the salad fork on the left side of the dinner for with prong facing up
set the dinner knife to the right of the charger with the blade facing up and toward the charger
set the tea spoon with the bowl facing up to the right of the knife
set the soup spoon with the bowl facing up right of the spoon
set the water glass top right of the charger
set the wine glass to the right of the wine glass
move the wine glass next to the blade of the knife
set the  coffee cup next to the wine glass
set bread plate top left of the charge above the forks
set the butter knife on the bread plate with the blade facing left
set the dessert fork between the bread plate and the water glass with the prongs facing right
set the dessert spoon between the dessert fork and charger with the bowl facing left
